item.description:
We assume you're running a Bitcoin node on Regtest. In case you're not and you're not sure how to configure your Bitcoin node to run on Regtest have a look at this guide.
Generate address 1bitcoin-cli getnewaddress Generate (mine) blocks bitcoin-cli generatetoaddress &lt;number of blocks&gt; &lt;youraddress&gt;
1bitcoin-cli generatetoaddress 50 bcrt1qywrq947s5yjjn7ye45y9wwh3g093cvec5fl9gn Note that after genering blocks the &quot;mining&quot; rewards can not be usued until they have matured. Rewards are considered matured after 100 confirmations.
